Mauritius Ex-Finance Minister Jugnauth Arrested, Radio One Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-09-22T12:03:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/mauritius-ex-finance-minister-jugnauth-arrested-radio-one-says.html
Mauritius’s former finance
minister, Pravind Jugnauth, was arrested by the country’s anti-
graft agency, Port Louis-based Radio One reported today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
